title: Skies clear, but California death toll expected to rise
text:
Skies clear, but California death toll expected to rise 8:39pm IST - 01:28 
The death toll in southern California's devastating floods and mudslides stood at 13 Wednesday morning but was expected to rise, even as the powerful storms that caused them moved out to sea. Colette Luke has more.
